{"ID":"20240201213647-7d0q2gm","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240201213647-7d0q2gm","title":"writing-technology-blog-six-years","updated":"20240201213647"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213648-t5iw9do","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213648-t5iw9do","updated":"20240201213648"}},{"ID":"20240201213649-vqk9meg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213649-vqk9meg","updated":"20240201213649"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"title: 坚持写技术博客六年了!"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"category: 走近作者"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"tag:"}]},{"ID":"20240201213650-btefpgc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213650-btefpgc","updated":"20240201213650"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213651-y3nz7ah","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213651-y3nz7ah","updated":"20240201213651"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213652-5nt7zrb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213652-5nt7zrb","updated":"20240201213652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"杂谈"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213653-224jtz4","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213653-224jtz4","updated":"20240201213653"}},{"ID":"20240201213654-tcx4i0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213654-tcx4i0k","updated":"20240201213654"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"坚持写技术博客已经有六年了，也算是一个小小的里程碑了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213655-nvglvxc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213655-nvglvxc","updated":"20240201213655"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一开始，我写技术博客就是简单地总结自己课堂上学习的课程比如网络、操作系统。渐渐地，我开始撰写一些更为系统化的知识点详解和面试常见问题总结。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213656-r055mub","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213656-r055mub","updated":"20240201213656"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"JavaGuide 首页","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230408131717766.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213657-np7521f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213657-np7521f","updated":"20240201213657"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"许多人都想写技术博客，但却不清楚这对他们有何好处。有些人开始写技术博客，却不知道如何坚持下去，也不知道该写些什么。这篇文章我会认真聊聊我对记录技术博客的一些看法和心得，或许可以帮助你解决这些问题。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213658-w7six8h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213658-w7six8h","updated":"20240201213658"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"写技术博客有哪些好处？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213659-114chh0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213659-114chh0","updated":"20240201213659"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学习效果更好，加深知识点的认识"}]},{"ID":"20240201213660-bkayzpw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213660-bkayzpw","updated":"20240201213660"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"费曼学习法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 大家应该已经比较清楚了，这是一个经过实践证明非常有效的学习方式。费曼学习法的命名源自 Richard Feynman，这位物理学家曾获得过诺贝尔物理学奖，也曾参与过曼哈顿计划。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213661-ahjmc0q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213661-ahjmc0q","updated":"20240201213661"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所谓费曼学习法，就是当你学习了一个新知识之后，想象自己是一个老师：用最简单、最浅显直白的话复述、表达复杂深奥的知识，最好不要使用行业术语，让非行业内的人也能听懂。为了达到这种效果，最好想象你是在给一个 80 多岁或 8 岁的小孩子上课，甚至他们都能听懂。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213662-fv9r6lk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213662-fv9r6lk","updated":"20240201213662"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"教授别人学习效果最好","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/v2-19373c2e61873c5083ee4b1d1523f8f5_720w.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213663-jsvsdvf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213663-jsvsdvf","updated":"20240201213663"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看书、看视频这类都属于是被动学习，学习效果比较差。费曼学习方法属于主动学习，学习效果非常好。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213664-iq6thiu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213664-iq6thiu","updated":"20240201213664"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"写技术博客实际就是教别人的一种方式。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 不过，记录技术博客的时候是可以有专业术语（除非你的文章群体是非技术人员），只是你需要用自己的话表述出来，尽量让别人一看就懂。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"切忌照搬书籍或者直接复制粘贴其他人的总结！"}]},{"ID":"20240201213665-fcb70up","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213665-fcb70up","updated":"20240201213665"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果我们被动的学习某个知识点，可能大部分时候都是仅仅满足自己能够会用的层面，你并不会深究其原理，甚至很多关键概念都没搞懂。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213666-8edwunm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213666-8edwunm","updated":"20240201213666"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你是要将你所学到的知识总结成一篇博客的话，一定会加深你对这个知识点的思考。很多时候，你为了将一个知识点讲清楚，你回去查阅很多资料，甚至需要查看很多源码，这些细小的积累在潜移默化中加深了你对这个知识点的认识。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213667-sk58no7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213667-sk58no7","updated":"20240201213667"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"甚至，我还经常会遇到这种情况："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"写博客的过程中，自己突然意识到自己对于某个知识点的理解存在错误。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213668-huojq44","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213668-huojq44","updated":"20240201213668"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"写博客本身就是一个对自己学习到的知识进行总结、回顾、思考的过程。记录博客也是对于自己学习历程的一种记录。随着时间的流逝、年龄的增长，这又何尝不是一笔宝贵的精神财富呢？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213669-wy28wi1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213669-wy28wi1","updated":"20240201213669"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知识星球的一位球友还提到写技术博客有助于完善自己的知识体系："}]},{"ID":"20240201213670-bdbn51t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213670-bdbn51t","updated":"20240201213670"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"写技术博客有助于完善自己的知识体系","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230408121336432.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213671-t7tuh7j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213671-t7tuh7j","updated":"20240201213671"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"帮助别人的同时获得成就感"}]},{"ID":"20240201213672-wethfl4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213672-wethfl4","updated":"20240201213672"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就像我们程序员希望自己的产品能够得到大家的认可和喜欢一样。我们写技术博客在某一方面当然也是为了能够得到别人的认可。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213673-ocxveci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213673-ocxveci","updated":"20240201213673"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当你写的东西对别人产生帮助的时候，你会产生成就感和幸福感。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213674-8srm9g2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213674-8srm9g2","updated":"20240201213674"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"读者的认可","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230404181906257.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213675-v0l5gnk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213675-v0l5gnk","updated":"20240201213675"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这种成就感和幸福感会作为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正向反馈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，继续激励你写博客。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213676-qoqg41r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213676-qoqg41r","updated":"20240201213676"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是，即使受到很多读者的赞赏，也要保持谦虚学习的太多。人外有人，比你技术更厉害的读者多了去，一定要虚心学习！"}]},{"ID":"20240201213677-m2epbe3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213677-m2epbe3","updated":"20240201213677"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当然，你可以可能会受到很多非议。可能会有很多人说你写的文章没有深度，还可能会有很多人说你闲的蛋疼，你写的东西网上/书上都有。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213678-10klvds","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213678-10klvds","updated":"20240201213678"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"坦然对待这些非议，做好自己，走好自己的路就好！用行动自证！"}]},{"ID":"20240201213679-s4mzj9d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213679-s4mzj9d","updated":"20240201213679"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可能会有额外的收入"}]},{"ID":"20240201213680-de1vqtf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213680-de1vqtf","updated":"20240201213680"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"写博客可能还会为你带来经济收入。输出价值的同时，还能够有合理的经济收入，这是最好的状态！"}]},{"ID":"20240201213681-wly2os1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213681-wly2os1","updated":"20240201213681"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么说是可能呢？ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"因为就目前来看，大部分人还是很难短期通过写博客有收入。我也不建议大家一开始写博客就奔着赚钱的目的，这样功利性太强了，效果可能反而不好。就比如说你坚持了写了半年发现赚不到钱，那你可能就会坚持不下去了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213682-8a3nyye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213682-8a3nyye","updated":"20240201213682"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我自己从大二开始写博客，大三下学期开始将自己的文章发布到公众号上，一直到大四下学期，才通过写博客赚到属于自己的第一笔钱。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213683-3s7mega","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213683-3s7mega","updated":"20240201213683"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一笔钱是通过微信公众号接某培训机构的推广获得的。没记错的话，当时通过这个推广为自己带来了大约 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"500"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 元的收入。虽然这不是很多，但对于还在上大学的我来说，这笔钱非常宝贵。那时我才知道，原来写作真的可以赚钱，这也让我更有动力去分享自己的写作。可惜的是，在接了两次这家培训机构的广告之后，它就倒闭了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213684-4chh31l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213684-4chh31l","updated":"20240201213684"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"之后，很长一段时间我都没有接到过广告。直到网易的课程合作找上门，一篇文章 1000 元，每个月接近一篇，发了接近两年，这也算是我在大学期间比较稳定的一份收入来源了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213685-oa0vs3f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213685-oa0vs3f","updated":"20240201213685"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"网易的课程合作","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230408115720135.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213686-lwxzavz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213686-lwxzavz","updated":"20240201213686"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老粉应该大部分都是通过 JavaGuide 这个项目认识我的，这是我在大三开始准备秋招面试时创建的一个项目。没想到这个项目竟然火了一把，一度霸占了 GitHub 榜单。可能当时国内这类开源文档教程类项目太少了，所以这个项目受欢迎程度非常高。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213687-5og5j2c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213687-5og5j2c","updated":"20240201213687"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"JavaGuide Star 趋势","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230408131849198.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213688-uroe315","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213688-uroe315","updated":"20240201213688"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"项目火了之后，有一个国内比较大的云服务公司找到我，说是要赞助 JavaGuide 这个项目。我既惊又喜，担心别人是骗子，反复确认合同之后，最终确定以每月 1000 元的费用在我的项目首页加上对方公司的 banner。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213689-srns12u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213689-srns12u","updated":"20240201213689"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"随着时间的推移，以及自己后来写了一些比较受欢迎、比较受众的文章，我的博客知名度也有所提升，通过写博客的收入也增加了不少。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213690-hg8z7hl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213690-hg8z7hl","updated":"20240201213690"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"增加个人影响力"}]},{"ID":"20240201213691-n64bg1b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213691-n64bg1b","updated":"20240201213691"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"写技术博客是一种展示自己技术水平和经验的方式，能够让更多的人了解你的专业领域知识和技能。持续分享优质的技术文章，一定能够在技术领域增加个人影响力，这一点是毋庸置疑的。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213692-aaavoyt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213692-aaavoyt","updated":"20240201213692"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有了个人影响力之后，不论是对你后面找工作，还是搞付费知识分享或者出书，都非常有帮助。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213693-f26vvjc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213693-f26vvjc","updated":"20240201213693"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"拿我自己来说，已经很多知名出版社的编辑找过我，协商出一本的书的事情。这种机会应该也是很多人梦寐以求的。不过，我都一一拒绝了，因为觉得自己远远没有达到能够写书的水平。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213694-qxtcjhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213694-qxtcjhu","updated":"20240201213694"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"电子工业出版社编辑邀约出书","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://oss.javaguide.cn/about-the-author/college-life/image-20230408121132211.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213695-kxmnpov","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213695-kxmnpov","updated":"20240201213695"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其实不出书最主要的原因还是自己嫌麻烦，整个流程的事情太多了。我自己又是比较佛系随性的人，平时也不想把时间都留给工作。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213696-eqswtqx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"202